Package: coastalclaw
Version: 0.6.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: nodejs (>= 22), npm, curl, git, sqlite3
Recommends: ollama
Maintainer: CoastalClaw contributors <hello@coastalclaw.io>
Homepage: https://github.com/CoastalCrypto/CoastalClaw_IO
Description: Private AI agent OS — runs on your hardware
 CoastalClaw is a self-hosted AI agent platform. It provides a configurable
 AI assistant with a web UI, multi-agent swarm, local vector memory, and
 voice pipeline. All inference runs on-premise; data never leaves the machine.
